      "message": "I explained the logic of UPN above - it should match hostnames in subdomains of the UPN domain. We cannot use ends_with as we want to ensure that the deepest domain part of the UPN domain also fully matchs, meaning if UPN is user@domain.com, so upn_domain_part is domain.com, it should match host.sub.domain.com, but should not match host.sub.mydomain.com, which would be the case with ends_with.",
